{"tid":1542093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有Twitter嘅手足，求進入","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T18:29:22.000Z","uid":261667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9848c3cab7085829a7bf9c5d569f120b815dbcc","tid":1542093,"uid":261667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:06.000Z","msg":"有Twitter嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉//<br />\n<br />\n在此懇求各位 花一點時間<br />\n因為呢個投票活動只有24小時<br />\n外國媒體開嘅投票活動問香港人是否接受呢一個撤回<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongHermit/status/1169216501502468097?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongHermit%2Fstatus%2F1169216501502468097%3Fs%3D19&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2a9704f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongHermit%2Fstatus%2F1169216501502468097%3Fs%3D19&h=ca8b0291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongHermit/status/1169216501502468097?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n我地最愛既外國記者搞左個公投。<br />\n問我地接唔接受呢個撤回<br />\n<br />\n大家立即用下面hashtags 通知全世界<br />\n<br />\n#FakeWithdraw<br />\n#WithdrawIsFake<br />\n#假撤回<br />\n<br />\nFacebook/Twitter/IG/留言<br />\n要聽日全世界新聞版都出「Fake Withdraw」係頭版"},{"pid":"abe1276d618b00d575a9d9760adba7236d7c5422","tid":1542093,"uid":261667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338f396f77bdec5a20e04929d05d10cbd9478b82","tid":1542093,"uid":261667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b26c54b8f52dc7305274f09a083431986abae7","tid":1542093,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />